title: Hobbies
text:
Flying - I enjoy flying. I have been flying out of the womb since I was a wee lad. No one else can fly so I must be quite adept.
Sword Fighting - I fight with swords in my sleep. I have not fought anyone in real life but I haven’t seen anyone fight in real life so I must be the best.
Cat - This one may not be a hobby but I enjoy petting my cat. He is the best in the world.
